The paper presents algorithms for Dueling Bandits, which is a problem in the field of machine learning and decision making. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also discusses regret bounds and complexity, which are topics in theoretical computer science, making cs.CC (Computational Complexity) a likely category as well. Finally, the paper conducts experiments on synthetic data, which falls under the category of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
